{"tid":2038946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国论坛头像——光复香港时代革命满文版","createTime":"2020-05-27T19:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T14:49:01.000Z","uid":334191,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f29fb7f04c4fc69128b8388e70210addc44d679f","tid":2038946,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:39:58.000Z","msg":"这是一个满文论坛，所以头像自然用满文：<br />\n左边：Sulfanga Hong Kong-i Jalin Uthai Dashalaki 光复香港，时代革命<br />\n右边：Senggi, Fa&scaron;&scaron;an, Yasai muke, Nei 鲜血、辛劳、眼泪和汗水 （邱吉尔演说）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgtDKPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgtDKPr.png&h=75729bd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0891e47c5c2402831737fb31b9e8ae7e87b1577f","tid":2038946,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:41:03.000Z","msg":"手足有冇諗過你嘅語言打外國戰線"},{"pid":"c8d80d86ec44d479035eed75040f1ce0331894cd","tid":2038946,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:04:45.000Z","msg":"翻译<br />\n1) &quot;Free Hong Kong. Revolution now!&quot; <br />\n2) &quot;Blood, toil, tears and sweat&quot;. <br />\n注释：<br />\nsulfan (freedom) &gt;&gt; sulfanga (free); Hong Kong-i (of Hong Kong); jalin (for), A-i jalin = for A; uthai (at once, right away); dasan (politics) + halan (change) &gt;&gt; dashalan (revolution) &gt;&gt; dashalaki (revolutionize); sengi (blood); fa&scaron;&scaron;an (toil) &gt;&gt; fa&scaron;&scaron;ambi (to work hard); yasai (of the eye) + muke (water) &gt;&gt; yasai muke (tears); nei (sweat)."},{"pid":"4394544065e74fd7fbf25d6c0353f6502d78d959","tid":2038946,"uid":309148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0891e47c5c2402831737fb31b9e8ae7e87b1577f","tid":2038946,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:41:03.000Z","msg":"手足有冇諗過你嘅語言打外國戰線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:09:51.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n唔係逼你做 而係如果手足有呢個capacity去做嘅話 大可一試"},{"pid":"1f5c370d839c246dcbe50d